<div class="container-full">
    <h2>Trail Upload</h2>

    <p id="uploadinfo"></p>
    <p id="uploaderror"></p>

    <p>You can upload any valid GPX file that you recorded with your phone or navigation system. GPX files created with
        other tools should work as well as long as they have altitude data set.<br>
        If you experience issues with the upload, just send us an email.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="container-full">
    <div data-region="upload"></div>
</div>

<div id="infoRow" style="display: none">
    <div class="container-full">
        <h3>Trail Info</h3>
        <p>Please provide some additional information for this trail.</p>

        <div id="formErrors"></div>

        <form id="infoForm" class="form-block" method="post" action="#/trails/upload">
            <div>
                <label for="name">Name</label> <input name="name" id="name_field" type="text"/>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="type">Track type</label>
                <select name="type">
                    {{# each trailTypes }}
                        <option value="{{ this }}">{{ this }}</option>
                    {{/each}}
                </select>
            </div>
            <div>
                <label for="description">Description</label> <textarea name="description" type="text" class="width-80"
                                                                       rows="8"
                                                                       placeholder="provide some characteristics of the trail, such as underground type and when you recorded it"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="#" class="button" id="saveBtn"><i class="fa fa-save"></i> Save trail</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="container-full">
        <h3>Map preview</h3>
    </div>
    <div data-region="map">
    </div>
</div>